{"tid":278973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人覺得泰國真係好恐怖？好邪門？","createTime":"2017-06-11T00:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T12:08:57.000Z","uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"930a7debc80959c6d68fbdbf958d1974136f00f0","tid":278973,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"唔撚係講笑，打完呢個post個topic已經覺得個背脊好陰寒<br />\n<br />\n泰國又四面佛、又養鬼仔咁<br />\n好似好多邪門嘢<br />\n<br />\n之前聽過有個女仔屋企信四面佛，<br />\n個女仔自己後來走去信基督定天主教<br />\n之後佢走去玩筆仙，點知鬼上身<br />\n最後話關四面佛事<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解咁多人去泰國玩，唔驚咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同人講我唔敢去泰國，點知佢答我：非洲你都敢自己去，泰國你反而驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"86300f20717a38a1ef63d47771b6f1f65414f7da","tid":278973,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:52:33.000Z","msg":"on79"},{"pid":"2a9c9f67c80295d6bc6c02ee29604221e43deebd","tid":278973,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on79</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d8c28ddb68c21e55abbb34a9e6e02873c22108","tid":278973,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:01:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"5d8bd072e88822e4ea93c0d952ed77c5fa77ef61","tid":278973,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"佢玩筆仙係關筆仙事<br />\n四面神係第二樣野<br />\n至於養鬼果堆 世界各地都大把"},{"pid":"a33ab1286d66becd010caeea10f095befa0f6941","tid":278973,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"認同，千祈唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：去過三次泰國，黎緊年尾再去"},{"pid":"e6907c760be6e3fece34b03776a6fe0c70f61512","tid":278973,"uid":100626,"like":1,"dislike":0,